	<itemBody>
		<p>Read the following sentences and complete them using the correct form of the verb in parentheses.
</p>
		<div>

		<p> 

		 <div>1. Tú <textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE" expectedLength="15"/> (dibujar) con lápices de colores.</div>
